OL,3,CGovernment appoints KC to lead Abedi
OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FThe Government has appointed Jonathan
OL,7,FHall KC to lead a review into how
OL,8,FManchester Arena plotter Hashem Abedi
OL,9,Fwas able to carry out a violent attack
OL,10,Fon four prison officers.
OL,12,FMr Hall, who is the current
OL,13,FIndependent Reviewer of Terrorism
OL,14,FLegislation, will chair the inquiry
OL,15,Finto the incident at HMP Frankland in
OL,16,FApril.
OL,18,FAbedi targeted staff with boiling oil
OL,19,Fand homemade weapons in a planned
OL,20,Fambush.
