OL,3,CGovernment appoints KC to lead Abedi
OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,7,Fthe review would examine the operation
OL,8,Fof separation centres ` units designed
OL,9,Fto manage the most dangerous extremist
OL,10,Fprisoners ` and whether they are fit
OL,11,Ffor purpose.
OL,13,F"I will do whatever it takes to
OL,14,Fprotect our brave prison officers,"
OL,15,Fshe said in a statement on Thursday.
OL,17,F"I have asked for the review to report
OL,18,Fback promptly, and to leave no stone
OL,19,Funturned so we can prevent such an
OL,20,Fincident ever happening again."
