OL,3,CGovernment appoints KC to lead Abedi
OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FThe review will consider whether the
OL,7,Finternal findings from the Abedi
OL,8,Fincident point to a need for changes
OL,9,Fin how extremist offenders are placed
OL,10,Finto separation centres.
OL,12,FIt will also assess the legal and
OL,13,Foperational framework underpinning
OL,14,Fthese units, including whether the
OL,15,Fright balance is being struck between
OL,16,Fsecurity and long-term offender
OL,17,Fmanagement.
