OL,3,CGovernment appoints KC to lead Abedi
OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FThe inquiry is expected to produce
OL,7,Frecommendations aimed at improving
OL,8,Ffrontline safety and reducing the risk
OL,9,Fof similar attacks.
OL,11,FAbedi, who was convicted over the 2017
OL,12,FManchester Arena bombing which killed
OL,13,F22 people, was transferred from
OL,14,FFrankland, in Durham, to Belmarsh
OL,15,Fprison in south-east London following
OL,16,Fthe attack last month.
