OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FThree prison officers were taken to
OL,7,Fhospital with serious injuries
OL,8,Ffollowing the incident. The attack has
OL,9,Ftriggered outrage among survivors and
OL,10,Fvictims' families.
OL,12,FMartin Hibbert, who was left with life-
OL,13,Fchanging injuries, said in an open
OL,14,Fletter to the Justice Secretary that
OL,15,Fthe incident represented a
OL,16,F"catastrophic failure" to protect both
OL,17,Fstaff and the public.
