OL,4,Cprison attack review
OL,6,FFamilies of five of those killed have
OL,7,Falso demanded Abedi be stripped of
OL,8,Fprivileges and denied access to
OL,9,Fanything that could be used as a
OL,10,Fweapon.
OL,12,FPrison Officers' Association chairman
OL,13,FMark Fairhurst, who will meet Ms
OL,14,FMahmood next week, said staff at
OL,15,FFrankland were "traumatised" and
OL,16,F"angry" about the incident.
